##
Kind: captions

00:00:02.637 --> 00:00:03.671 position:21% line:89% align:start
[singing in Japanese]

00:01:11.673 --> 00:01:12.707 position:21% line:89% align:start
[singing in Japanese]

00:01:31.893 --> 00:01:34.696 position:7% line:83% align:start
[operator 1] Target has entered
the fourth sector.

00:01:34.729 --> 00:01:37.699 position:16% line:83% align:start
The ignorant moth flicks
closer to the flame, sir.

00:01:37.732 --> 00:01:41.703 position:19% line:83% align:start
This is the conclusion
of its final voyage.

00:01:45.707 --> 00:01:48.275 position:19% line:83% align:start
Two kilometers to reach
the Kermodec Trench.

00:01:48.308 --> 00:01:50.210 position:24% line:83% align:start
-Send out a pulse.
-Aye, aye, sir.

00:01:56.416 --> 00:01:58.285 position:30% line:89% align:start
[alarm beeping]

00:01:58.318 --> 00:02:00.755 position:33% line:83% align:start
Captain Nemo,
the enemy fleet has deployed

00:02:00.788 --> 00:02:02.690 position:21% line:83% align:start
six Garfish submarine
battleships

00:02:02.724 --> 00:02:04.391 position:24% line:83% align:start
from ten o'clock to
two o'clock.

00:02:04.424 --> 00:02:05.793 position:19% line:89% align:start
Six of them versus us?

00:02:05.827 --> 00:02:07.528 position:10% line:89% align:start
This is gonna be a tough one.

00:02:07.562 --> 00:02:10.364 position:13% line:83% align:start
What's worse is that we can
be sure that there are more

00:02:10.397 --> 00:02:12.399 position:27% line:83% align:start
on our flank and
beyond our sonar.

00:02:12.432 --> 00:02:14.869 position:13% line:83% align:start
This is what you would call
a tight pinch, sir.

00:02:15.570 --> 00:02:17.805 position:7% line:83% align:start
[operator 2]Target has entered
the third sector.

00:02:17.839 --> 00:02:20.140 position:13% line:89% align:start
Proceed with Operation D-2.

00:02:20.340 --> 00:02:21.408 position:35% line:89% align:start
Understood.

00:02:21.441 --> 00:02:22.910 position:30% line:89% align:start
As you command.

00:02:22.944 --> 00:02:24.612 position:16% line:83% align:start
[operator 1] Garfish six
through twelve,

00:02:24.646 --> 00:02:26.413 position:13% line:89% align:start
proceed with Operation D-2.

00:02:27.347 --> 00:02:30.183 position:13% line:89% align:start
[suspenseful music playing]

00:02:31.786 --> 00:02:33.621 position:27% line:83% align:start
They're flooding
their Torpedo tubes.

00:02:33.655 --> 00:02:35.422 position:16% line:89% align:start
Distance 2.2 kilometers.

00:02:35.455 --> 00:02:36.691 position:24% line:89% align:start
[missiles hissing]

00:02:36.724 --> 00:02:38.258 position:30% line:89% align:start
Torpedoes away.

00:02:38.291 --> 00:02:39.861 position:24% line:83% align:start
Twenty-four closing
at two kilometers.

00:02:39.894 --> 00:02:42.329 position:41% line:83% align:start
They're
creating a Torpedo storm.

00:02:43.831 --> 00:02:46.333 position:5% line:89% align:start
Sixty seconds until impact, sir.

00:02:46.366 --> 00:02:48.836 position:10% line:83% align:start
-Launch battle counterstrike.
-Aye, aye, sir.

00:02:48.870 --> 00:02:50.905 position:24% line:89% align:start
[missiles hissing]

00:02:54.709 --> 00:02:57.512 position:35% line:89% align:start
[explosion]

00:03:01.481 --> 00:03:02.784 position:38% line:89% align:start
No good.

00:03:02.817 --> 00:03:04.217 position:30% line:83% align:start
They've broken
through the barrier.

00:03:04.251 --> 00:03:05.452 position:13% line:89% align:start
Bring all engines to full.

00:03:05.485 --> 00:03:07.254 position:24% line:89% align:start
Descend and evade.

00:03:07.287 --> 00:03:08.923 position:30% line:89% align:start
[ship revving]

00:03:09.824 --> 00:03:11.526 position:24% line:89% align:start
[missiles hissing]

00:03:12.359 --> 00:03:14.261 position:30% line:83% align:start
Twenty seconds
to impact, Captain.

00:03:14.294 --> 00:03:16.329 position:27% line:83% align:start
Scrape our belly
on the sea floor, helmsmen.

00:03:16.363 --> 00:03:18.766 position:30% line:89% align:start
[ship revving]

00:03:21.301 --> 00:03:21.936 position:38% line:89% align:start
Ten, sir.

00:03:24.972 --> 00:03:27.675 position:24% line:89% align:start
[missiles hissing]

00:03:27.709 --> 00:03:29.677 position:16% line:89% align:start
Four passed over us, sir.

00:03:29.711 --> 00:03:30.945 position:19% line:89% align:start
There's still one more.

00:03:32.513 --> 00:03:34.347 position:35% line:89% align:start
[explosion]

00:03:35.750 --> 00:03:37.585 position:38% line:89% align:start
[screams]

00:03:43.691 --> 00:03:45.860 position:27% line:89% align:start
[exhales deeply]

00:03:45.893 --> 00:03:47.862 position:7% line:89% align:start
That was a good plan, Captain.

00:03:47.895 --> 00:03:49.997 position:13% line:83% align:start
If we were any higher, we'd
be sleeping with the fishes.

00:03:51.331 --> 00:03:53.701 position:27% line:83% align:start
-Damage report?
-Engines are secure.

00:03:53.735 --> 00:03:56.303 position:30% line:83% align:start
There's a small
leak in the stern.

00:03:56.336 --> 00:03:58.639 position:41% line:83% align:start
What is
the status of the Garfish?

00:03:58.673 --> 00:03:59.807 position:33% line:89% align:start
[alarm beeps]

00:03:59.841 --> 00:04:01.308 position:35% line:83% align:start
We have six
approaching from the bow

00:04:01.341 --> 00:04:02.810 position:38% line:83% align:start
and four
approaching at two o'clock.

00:04:02.844 --> 00:04:05.613 position:27% line:83% align:start
Relative velocity
is approximately eight knots.

00:04:06.379 --> 00:04:07.515 position:35% line:89% align:start
All right.

00:04:07.548 --> 00:04:09.349 position:16% line:89% align:start
Let's go, First Officer.

00:04:10.685 --> 00:04:13.386 position:13% line:83% align:start
Give every tube a full load
of missiles and depth charges

00:04:13.420 --> 00:04:14.856 position:10% line:89% align:start
and begin flooding the tubes.

00:04:14.889 --> 00:04:17.357 position:33% line:83% align:start
Torpedo tubes
are now flooding, sir.

00:04:21.562 --> 00:04:23.865 position:21% line:83% align:start
Deploy depth charges
to starboard side

00:04:23.898 --> 00:04:25.032 position:21% line:89% align:start
then take a 10-count

00:04:25.066 --> 00:04:26.801 position:21% line:83% align:start
and fire missiles at
secondary target.

00:04:26.834 --> 00:04:27.869 position:24% line:89% align:start
[Electra] Aye, aye.

00:04:29.737 --> 00:04:31.438 position:24% line:89% align:start
[missiles chugging]

00:04:31.471 --> 00:04:33.541 position:33% line:83% align:start
[wireless 1]
Tubes are fully loaded.

00:04:33.574 --> 00:04:35.510 position:10% line:83% align:start
[wireless 2] Port tubes ready
for initial firing.

00:04:35.543 --> 00:04:37.545 position:13% line:83% align:start
Targeting error correction
is complete.

00:04:37.578 --> 00:04:39.046 position:44% line:89% align:start
Fire.

00:04:39.080 --> 00:04:40.915 position:24% line:89% align:start
[missiles hissing]

00:04:48.923 --> 00:04:50.758 position:19% line:83% align:start
Sir, the depth charges
had been launched.

00:04:50.792 --> 00:04:52.827 position:24% line:89% align:start
[missiles hissing]

00:04:57.397 --> 00:04:59.033 position:35% line:89% align:start
[explosion]

00:05:02.837 --> 00:05:06.406 position:7% line:83% align:start
I confirm multiple explosions,
total of six.

00:05:06.439 --> 00:05:07.575 position:19% line:89% align:start
That leaves four more.

00:05:07.608 --> 00:05:09.977 position:33% line:89% align:start
[explosions]

00:05:10.545 --> 00:05:11.979 position:30% line:83% align:start
Four explosions
confirmed, Captain.

00:05:12.013 --> 00:05:13.881 position:21% line:89% align:start
No further readings.

00:05:13.915 --> 00:05:16.684 position:5% line:83% align:start
[Electra] All identified Garfish
have been thoroughly destroyed.

00:05:22.123 --> 00:05:24.659 position:5% line:89% align:start
They sent 10 after us this time.

00:05:24.692 --> 00:05:26.861 position:24% line:83% align:start
The Neo-Atlanteans
are certainly getting bolder.

00:05:26.894 --> 00:05:28.563 position:21% line:89% align:start
[Nemo] First Officer,

00:05:28.596 --> 00:05:30.698 position:16% line:83% align:start
how much of our offensive
weaponry is still intact?

00:05:30.731 --> 00:05:32.066 position:30% line:89% align:start
We are at 30%.

00:05:32.099 --> 00:05:34.068 position:38% line:83% align:start
Remaining
munition's loading now.

00:05:36.469 --> 00:05:38.639 position:33% line:83% align:start
[Nemo] Sonar,
where are the others?

00:05:38.673 --> 00:05:41.642 position:19% line:83% align:start
I'm detecting five more
but it's extremely odd.

00:05:41.676 --> 00:05:43.544 position:10% line:89% align:start
They're all leaving the area.

00:05:44.444 --> 00:05:46.379 position:16% line:83% align:start
They must be falling back
to attack positions.

00:05:46.413 --> 00:05:47.849 position:35% line:89% align:start
I doubt it.

00:05:47.882 --> 00:05:50.483 position:19% line:83% align:start
They're all moving out
of their firing range, ma'am.

00:05:50.518 --> 00:05:53.988 position:10% line:83% align:start
-Are they leaving us behind?
-Not very likely.

00:05:54.021 --> 00:05:55.957 position:16% line:83% align:start
Stay alert for an attack
from the surface.

00:05:55.990 --> 00:05:57.558 position:30% line:89% align:start
[Electra] Aye.

00:05:57.592 --> 00:06:00.061 position:24% line:83% align:start
Prepare for attack,
this one from above.

00:06:05.566 --> 00:06:07.434 position:33% line:83% align:start
[operator 1]
The Nautilus has been sighted.

00:06:07.467 --> 00:06:09.103 position:24% line:83% align:start
[operator 2] It is
within firing range.

00:06:09.136 --> 00:06:11.639 position:10% line:89% align:start
You have my gratitude, Nemo,

00:06:11.672 --> 00:06:14.842 position:27% line:83% align:start
for volunteering
for my experiment.

00:06:14.876 --> 00:06:17.678 position:16% line:83% align:start
-Begin Operation Sea Net.
-Understood.

00:06:17.712 --> 00:06:19.780 position:10% line:83% align:start
[female operator] Proceeding
to Phase Two.

00:06:19.814 --> 00:06:21.716 position:10% line:83% align:start
[operator 1] Prepare the Sea
Net Beam Gun.

00:06:21.749 --> 00:06:24.552 position:13% line:89% align:start
[suspenseful music playing]

00:06:28.556 --> 00:06:30.091 position:7% line:89% align:start
[operator 3] Main tube is open.

00:06:30.124 --> 00:06:32.126 position:7% line:89% align:start
[operator 4] Lowering beam gun.

00:06:33.761 --> 00:06:35.663 position:24% line:89% align:start
[beam gun whirring]

00:06:39.934 --> 00:06:42.069 position:7% line:89% align:start
[operator 2] Beam gun is ready.

00:06:42.103 --> 00:06:43.537 position:27% line:83% align:start
[female operator]
Power transferring.

00:06:43.571 --> 00:06:46.007 position:33% line:83% align:start
[operator 3]
Magnetic field stable.

00:06:46.040 --> 00:06:47.541 position:7% line:89% align:start
[operator 1] Targets acquired.

00:06:47.575 --> 00:06:48.876 position:13% line:89% align:start
[follower 1] Ready to fire.

00:06:48.910 --> 00:06:50.077 position:44% line:89% align:start
Good.

00:06:50.111 --> 00:06:52.013 position:21% line:89% align:start
Release the Sea Net.

00:07:04.025 --> 00:07:05.760 position:16% line:89% align:start
Good Lord. What is that?

00:07:05.793 --> 00:07:08.963 position:13% line:83% align:start
Sir, the nautilus has been
surrounded by a magnetic field.

00:07:11.732 --> 00:07:13.734 position:13% line:89% align:start
He's got a hold of us now.

00:07:13.768 --> 00:07:16.570 position:19% line:83% align:start
Gargoyle has completed
the Sea Net beam gun.

00:07:16.604 --> 00:07:21.542 position:10% line:83% align:start
Well, Nemo, will you be able
to escape from my new weapon?

00:07:26.280 --> 00:07:28.182 position:27% line:83% align:start
He's dragging the
ship to the surface.

00:07:28.215 --> 00:07:29.482 position:24% line:89% align:start
Lock trim downward.

00:07:29.517 --> 00:07:30.918 position:19% line:89% align:start
Blow open the aft tank.

00:07:30.952 --> 00:07:32.887 position:35% line:83% align:start
We'll be in
a vertical list, sir.

00:07:32.920 --> 00:07:34.088 position:33% line:89% align:start
I know that.

00:07:34.121 --> 00:07:35.623 position:5% line:89% align:start
It's our only chance for escape.

00:07:40.695 --> 00:07:42.897 position:19% line:83% align:start
All hands, prepare for
severe listing!

00:07:42.930 --> 00:07:45.967 position:35% line:89% align:start
[screaming]

00:07:50.137 --> 00:07:53.074 position:7% line:83% align:start
Please remind me to have a few
words with the steering crew.

00:08:00.281 --> 00:08:01.215 position:16% line:89% align:start
All engines ahead, full!

00:08:06.787 --> 00:08:08.723 position:10% line:89% align:start
Hmph. What a futile attempt.

00:08:08.756 --> 00:08:10.191 position:33% line:83% align:start
[operator 1]
Power generating at 80%.

00:08:25.606 --> 00:08:26.707 position:30% line:89% align:start
That's no good.

00:08:26.741 --> 00:08:28.075 position:35% line:83% align:start
The engines
can't defeat the field.

00:08:28.109 --> 00:08:30.778 position:21% line:83% align:start
Bring all engines to
maximum capacity!

00:08:30.811 --> 00:08:32.246 position:10% line:89% align:start
[engineer] That's impossible!

00:08:32.279 --> 00:08:34.048 position:16% line:83% align:start
The screws can't take on
any more stress!

00:08:34.081 --> 00:08:35.182 position:24% line:89% align:start
Don't tell me that!

00:08:35.583 --> 00:08:37.618 position:16% line:83% align:start
[Electra] We're 30 meters
from the surface.

00:08:40.821 --> 00:08:42.289 position:35% line:89% align:start
Excellent.

00:08:42.690 --> 00:08:43.924 position:21% line:89% align:start
Come to me, Nautilus.

00:08:43.958 --> 00:08:45.126 position:30% line:89% align:start
Show yourself.

00:08:58.305 --> 00:08:59.940 position:5% line:83% align:start
-What on earth is happening now?
-[King whines]

00:08:59.974 --> 00:09:01.275 position:10% line:89% align:start
The ship's out of the water.

00:09:05.713 --> 00:09:08.049 position:16% line:83% align:start
There's some sort of ship
directly overhead.

00:09:11.786 --> 00:09:14.355 position:13% line:83% align:start
-What in the world is that?
-Amazing.

00:09:14.388 --> 00:09:16.290 position:27% line:83% align:start
Gargoyle's built
a flying battleship.

00:09:22.096 --> 00:09:24.632 position:30% line:83% align:start
Someone tell us
what's happening now!

00:09:24.665 --> 00:09:26.967 position:27% line:83% align:start
Civilians are not
allowed on the bridge!

00:09:27.001 --> 00:09:30.604 position:10% line:83% align:start
I don't care about your silly
rules right now, blondie.

00:09:30.638 --> 00:09:33.607 position:19% line:83% align:start
We have a right to know
what we're involved in.

00:09:34.708 --> 00:09:35.810 position:16% line:83% align:start
-[Sanson] Well, would you
look at that.

00:09:35.843 --> 00:09:36.710 position:30% line:83% align:start
-[Marie] We're
flying in the sky.

00:09:36.744 --> 00:09:38.779 position:16% line:83% align:start
[Hanson] That big magnet
has a hold of us.

00:09:38.813 --> 00:09:40.881 position:21% line:83% align:start
How can that ship fly
without forward movement?

00:09:43.084 --> 00:09:44.685 position:16% line:89% align:start
[Grandis] What are those?

00:09:47.888 --> 00:09:49.690 position:10% line:89% align:start
[operator 2] Atomic vibration

00:09:49.723 --> 00:09:51.659 position:16% line:83% align:start
and supersonic wave guns
are in position.

00:09:51.692 --> 00:09:53.894 position:24% line:83% align:start
Final preparations
have been made.

00:09:53.928 --> 00:09:56.197 position:16% line:83% align:start
[follower 1] We are ready
to test the weapon.

00:09:56.230 --> 00:09:57.798 position:19% line:89% align:start
This is the technology

00:09:57.832 --> 00:10:00.167 position:27% line:83% align:start
that brought down
the walls of Jericho.

00:10:00.201 --> 00:10:01.402 position:44% line:89% align:start
Yes.

00:10:01.435 --> 00:10:03.404 position:44% line:89% align:start
Nemo.

00:10:03.437 --> 00:10:05.339 position:13% line:83% align:start
Please accept my invitation
to hell

00:10:05.372 --> 00:10:07.007 position:35% line:83% align:start
for you and
your pathetic crew.

00:10:07.041 --> 00:10:09.310 position:10% line:83% align:start
[female operator] Our target
will be the space titanium alloy

00:10:09.343 --> 00:10:10.678 position:21% line:89% align:start
on the Nautilus hull.

00:10:10.711 --> 00:10:12.012 position:24% line:83% align:start
[operator 3] Proper
pitch is attained.

00:10:12.046 --> 00:10:14.281 position:13% line:83% align:start
[operator 1] Maximum energy
is attained.

00:10:14.315 --> 00:10:16.350 position:10% line:83% align:start
[female operator] All systems
are at optimal performance.

00:10:16.383 --> 00:10:17.885 position:21% line:89% align:start
[follower 1] Firing.

00:10:27.728 --> 00:10:30.664 position:13% line:89% align:start
My word, what's that sound?

00:10:30.698 --> 00:10:33.100 position:13% line:83% align:start
The ship is being bombarded
with electrical waves.

00:10:33.134 --> 00:10:35.202 position:10% line:89% align:start
I wonder what those are for.

00:10:35.236 --> 00:10:37.304 position:13% line:89% align:start
[electrical waves buzzing]

00:10:43.410 --> 00:10:45.246 position:35% line:89% align:start
[cracking]

00:10:47.047 --> 00:10:48.949 position:30% line:89% align:start
[alarm ringing]

00:10:48.983 --> 00:10:50.417 position:7% line:83% align:start
[engineer] The armored plating
on the bow is cracking apart.

00:10:50.451 --> 00:10:52.186 position:24% line:89% align:start
That's impossible.

00:10:52.219 --> 00:10:54.088 position:16% line:83% align:start
More cracks are appearing
on our stern and lower hull.

00:10:58.792 --> 00:11:01.228 position:7% line:89% align:start
So, an atomic vibration device.

00:11:01.262 --> 00:11:03.731 position:16% line:83% align:start
You have been very busy,
haven't you, Gargoyle?

00:11:03.764 --> 00:11:05.399 position:44% line:89% align:start
Hmph.

00:11:05.432 --> 00:11:07.301 position:16% line:83% align:start
I'm amazed that you have
withstood it

00:11:07.334 --> 00:11:08.369 position:21% line:89% align:start
this long, Nautilus.

00:11:20.147 --> 00:11:21.815 position:13% line:83% align:start
[engineer] The bow's outer
layer of armor

00:11:21.849 --> 00:11:23.050 position:7% line:89% align:start
has been peeled away, Captain.

00:11:23.083 --> 00:11:25.019 position:13% line:83% align:start
[sonar] Primary power lines
are shut down.

00:11:25.052 --> 00:11:28.055 position:10% line:83% align:start
-Captain, what are we to do?
-Hit them with a volley.

00:11:28.088 --> 00:11:29.123 position:27% line:89% align:start
We'll fight back.

00:11:32.459 --> 00:11:34.295 position:35% line:89% align:start
[explosion]

00:11:36.263 --> 00:11:37.331 position:24% line:89% align:start
He's well-defended.

00:11:38.633 --> 00:11:40.367 position:7% line:83% align:start
Our anti-aircraft weapons will
be useless against his barrier.

00:11:46.073 --> 00:11:48.309 position:35% line:89% align:start
[explosion]

00:11:48.342 --> 00:11:50.444 position:10% line:83% align:start
[engineer] Our reserve plane
has been destroyed!

00:11:51.946 --> 00:11:53.147 position:38% line:89% align:start
Stop it.

00:11:53.180 --> 00:11:55.115 position:21% line:83% align:start
They're destroying us
one inch at a time.

00:11:55.149 --> 00:11:57.785 position:35% line:89% align:start
[explosion]

00:11:58.385 --> 00:11:59.987 position:7% line:89% align:start
[engineer] Third block damaged.

00:12:00.020 --> 00:12:02.089 position:5% line:89% align:start
Powder magazines have detonated.

00:12:02.122 --> 00:12:04.458 position:13% line:83% align:start
Ah. The fire control system
is being destroyed.

00:12:08.429 --> 00:12:10.264 position:19% line:83% align:start
The engine is straining
under this load, sir.

00:12:12.099 --> 00:12:13.500 position:47% line:89% align:start
No!

00:12:13.535 --> 00:12:15.269 position:27% line:89% align:start
Oh, no. What now?

00:12:15.302 --> 00:12:18.372 position:7% line:83% align:start
[engineer] Main electric power
systems are offline.

00:12:18.405 --> 00:12:20.274 position:16% line:89% align:start
This can't be happening.

00:12:20.307 --> 00:12:21.742 position:7% line:89% align:start
Looks like the end of the line.

00:12:26.080 --> 00:12:28.849 position:19% line:83% align:start
[operator] The Nautilus
has fallen silent.

00:12:28.882 --> 00:12:29.950 position:35% line:89% align:start
Thank you.

00:12:29.984 --> 00:12:31.051 position:27% line:89% align:start
Halt the attack.

00:12:31.085 --> 00:12:32.520 position:5% line:89% align:start
Put me in contact with the ship.

00:12:32.554 --> 00:12:34.922 position:30% line:83% align:start
I wish to speak
with the Captain.

00:12:34.955 --> 00:12:35.789 position:35% line:89% align:start
Understood.

00:12:39.126 --> 00:12:41.128 position:38% line:89% align:start
[beeping]

00:12:41.161 --> 00:12:44.231 position:13% line:83% align:start
We're receiving a wireless
message from the battleship.

00:12:44.265 --> 00:12:45.766 position:24% line:83% align:start
-Patch it through.
-Aye, sir.

00:12:47.067 --> 00:12:49.203 position:21% line:83% align:start
[Gargoyle] It's been
a long time, Nemo.

00:12:50.104 --> 00:12:51.305 position:35% line:89% align:start
Foul demon.

00:12:51.338 --> 00:12:53.340 position:33% line:83% align:start
-Is that you?
-Hmph.

00:12:53.374 --> 00:12:56.176 position:5% line:89% align:start
You haven't changed in 13 years.

00:12:56.210 --> 00:12:58.212 position:19% line:89% align:start
Still so terribly rude.

00:12:58.245 --> 00:13:00.281 position:10% line:89% align:start
That is none of your concern.

00:13:00.314 --> 00:13:01.516 position:24% line:89% align:start
[Gargoyle] Correct.

00:13:01.549 --> 00:13:03.350 position:27% line:89% align:start
Act as you wish.

00:13:03.384 --> 00:13:04.918 position:21% line:89% align:start
You'll soon be dead.

00:13:04.952 --> 00:13:08.122 position:13% line:83% align:start
We never did get to finish
our chess match.

00:13:08.155 --> 00:13:11.091 position:27% line:83% align:start
How unfortunate,
unless you'd like to do so now.

00:13:11.125 --> 00:13:13.160 position:35% line:83% align:start
There's no
reason for that, Gargoyle.

00:13:13.193 --> 00:13:15.095 position:27% line:89% align:start
I've already won.

00:13:15.129 --> 00:13:18.566 position:7% line:83% align:start
[Gargoyle] As stubborn as ever,
old friend.

00:13:18.600 --> 00:13:20.834 position:7% line:89% align:start
I regret not seeing you again,

00:13:20.868 --> 00:13:24.938 position:7% line:83% align:start
but you are to blame for never
trying to see things my way.

00:13:24.972 --> 00:13:26.940 position:19% line:89% align:start
Well, good night, Nemo.

00:13:26.974 --> 00:13:29.376 position:16% line:89% align:start
Sleep peacefully forever.

00:13:29.410 --> 00:13:31.979 position:24% line:83% align:start
Rest in your gilded
coffin with your crew.

00:13:32.012 --> 00:13:34.214 position:38% line:89% align:start
[laughs]

00:13:39.320 --> 00:13:41.455 position:35% line:83% align:start
-Damn him!
-I guess this is it.

00:13:45.392 --> 00:13:47.428 position:13% line:83% align:start
[Electra] There's only one
possible way to win, sir.

00:13:47.461 --> 00:13:48.563 position:41% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

00:13:48.596 --> 00:13:50.197 position:16% line:89% align:start
We must scuttle the ship.

00:13:50.230 --> 00:13:53.535 position:16% line:89% align:start
â™ª The Secret Blue Water

00:13:54.502 --> 00:13:55.603 position:41% line:89% align:start
[thuds]

00:13:56.805 --> 00:13:59.973 position:10% line:83% align:start
Sir, can't you see that this
is our best and only chance?

00:14:00.007 --> 00:14:01.543 position:21% line:83% align:start
That is not merely a
battleship above us,

00:14:01.576 --> 00:14:04.011 position:21% line:89% align:start
but Gargoyle as well.

00:14:04.044 --> 00:14:06.146 position:19% line:83% align:start
Are we going to pass up
this golden opportunity

00:14:06.180 --> 00:14:07.582 position:19% line:89% align:start
to achieve our purpose?

00:14:07.615 --> 00:14:10.017 position:5% line:83% align:start
If we self-destruct the particle
annihilation engine,

00:14:10.050 --> 00:14:12.252 position:7% line:89% align:start
everything will be obliterated.

00:14:12.286 --> 00:14:15.155 position:7% line:89% align:start
We must do this, Captain Nemo.

00:14:15.189 --> 00:14:17.858 position:16% line:83% align:start
We've lived for 13 years
for a moment like this.

00:14:19.193 --> 00:14:21.228 position:5% line:89% align:start
What is wrong with you, Captain?

00:14:21.261 --> 00:14:23.364 position:19% line:89% align:start
Make up your mind now.

00:14:25.366 --> 00:14:28.503 position:13% line:83% align:start
You used to make decisions
so quickly, but you've changed.

00:14:28.536 --> 00:14:31.038 position:41% line:89% align:start
Sir...

00:14:31.071 --> 00:14:33.907 position:30% line:83% align:start
do you know why
this has happened to us?

00:14:33.941 --> 00:14:35.309 position:33% line:83% align:start
Shall I tell
you the reason, sir?

00:14:36.511 --> 00:14:38.278 position:19% line:83% align:start
-It's Nadia, isn't it?
-Mm?

00:14:38.312 --> 00:14:40.948 position:13% line:83% align:start
You couldn't stand to harm
a hair on her precious head.

00:14:40.981 --> 00:14:42.416 position:27% line:89% align:start
Hold your tongue!

00:14:42.449 --> 00:14:44.418 position:10% line:83% align:start
Kill yourself if that's what
you really want.

00:14:44.451 --> 00:14:46.019 position:10% line:89% align:start
But don't make that decision

00:14:46.053 --> 00:14:47.622 position:24% line:83% align:start
for the rest of us,
if you don't mind.

00:14:47.655 --> 00:14:51.024 position:7% line:83% align:start
While you're on board, you will
obey the rules of this ship.

00:14:51.058 --> 00:14:53.293 position:21% line:89% align:start
Mm, I don't think so.

00:14:53.327 --> 00:14:54.529 position:30% line:89% align:start
Oh, you don't?

00:14:54.562 --> 00:14:57.699 position:19% line:83% align:start
Well, our sworn mission
is to exterminate

00:14:57.732 --> 00:14:59.933 position:5% line:89% align:start
the Neo-Atlanteans at all costs.

00:14:59.967 --> 00:15:02.202 position:19% line:83% align:start
Do you know why you act
this way, you idiot?

00:15:02.236 --> 00:15:03.937 position:41% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

00:15:03.971 --> 00:15:05.707 position:30% line:83% align:start
You want to die
with Captain Nemo

00:15:05.740 --> 00:15:07.374 position:27% line:83% align:start
because you know
he will never love you.

00:15:07.675 --> 00:15:10.244 position:30% line:83% align:start
That's the real
reason, isn't it?

00:15:10.277 --> 00:15:12.179 position:41% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

00:15:12.212 --> 00:15:15.315 position:16% line:83% align:start
So forgive me if I choose
to find a way for us to live.

00:15:15.349 --> 00:15:19.253 position:10% line:83% align:start
Unlike you, I have something
to live for, you ridiculous nit.

00:15:19.286 --> 00:15:21.589 position:10% line:83% align:start
If you want to kill yourself
then leave me out!

00:15:25.225 --> 00:15:27.194 position:30% line:83% align:start
-Let's go boys.
-All right.

00:15:27.227 --> 00:15:30.264 position:10% line:83% align:start
We can take care of ourselves
and the Katherine, Ms. Electra.

00:15:30.297 --> 00:15:32.499 position:27% line:83% align:start
You see, I don't
want to die today either.

00:15:32.534 --> 00:15:34.536 position:30% line:89% align:start
So, toodle-pip.

00:15:35.235 --> 00:15:37.271 position:41% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

00:15:37.304 --> 00:15:38.305 position:27% line:89% align:start
Hey, wait for me.

00:15:38.338 --> 00:15:39.607 position:33% line:89% align:start
I want to go.

00:15:39.641 --> 00:15:41.175 position:38% line:89% align:start
[groans]

00:15:41.208 --> 00:15:43.545 position:30% line:83% align:start
I'd hate to ask
you a stupid question.

00:15:43.578 --> 00:15:47.014 position:5% line:83% align:start
But the Gratan isn't going to be
drawn to the magnet, is it?

00:15:47.047 --> 00:15:49.116 position:16% line:89% align:start
[chuckles] Look at this.

00:15:49.149 --> 00:15:52.419 position:7% line:83% align:start
This gun is made of iron but it
isn't being drawn to it, is it?

00:15:52.453 --> 00:15:56.056 position:10% line:83% align:start
They clearly built that huge
magnet to attract only the alloy

00:15:56.089 --> 00:15:57.559 position:33% line:83% align:start
that makes up
the ship's plating.

00:15:57.592 --> 00:15:59.561 position:13% line:89% align:start
Why didn't I think of that?

00:15:59.594 --> 00:16:01.261 position:30% line:83% align:start
Are you really
going to escape from here?

00:16:01.295 --> 00:16:02.764 position:38% line:89% align:start
Well, no.

00:16:02.797 --> 00:16:05.399 position:7% line:83% align:start
I only said that to look bully
in front of Nemo.

00:16:05.432 --> 00:16:07.602 position:5% line:89% align:start
We're gonna cut this ship loose.

00:16:07.635 --> 00:16:09.136 position:16% line:83% align:start
There's no way in heaven
or Earth

00:16:09.169 --> 00:16:11.138 position:27% line:83% align:start
I'm going to let
that ignorant girl

00:16:11.171 --> 00:16:13.407 position:35% line:83% align:start
die with my
beloved Captain Nemo.

00:16:13.440 --> 00:16:14.676 position:30% line:89% align:start
Absolutely not.

00:16:14.709 --> 00:16:16.210 position:24% line:89% align:start
Yes, that's right.

00:16:16.243 --> 00:16:18.145 position:16% line:83% align:start
You should never give up
without a fight.

00:16:19.547 --> 00:16:20.648 position:30% line:89% align:start
Of course not.

00:16:20.682 --> 00:16:22.449 position:16% line:89% align:start
We won't kill ourselves.

00:16:22.483 --> 00:16:26.286 position:13% line:83% align:start
We have to devise some way
to survive until the very end.

00:16:26.320 --> 00:16:28.523 position:7% line:89% align:start
How do you propose we do that?

00:16:28.556 --> 00:16:30.424 position:33% line:83% align:start
We only have
one missile on board.

00:16:30.457 --> 00:16:33.628 position:5% line:83% align:start
Not only that, but the launching
tube has been disabled,

00:16:33.661 --> 00:16:36.063 position:27% line:83% align:start
so please tell me
how we can counterattack!

00:16:36.096 --> 00:16:38.265 position:27% line:83% align:start
How do we get out
from under this rotter

00:16:38.298 --> 00:16:40.802 position:10% line:83% align:start
without getting our knickers
dirty in the process?

00:16:40.835 --> 00:16:42.102 position:24% line:83% align:start
-Leave that to us!
-Leave that to us!

00:16:42.135 --> 00:16:43.505 position:38% line:89% align:start
[laughs]

00:16:43.538 --> 00:16:45.472 position:19% line:89% align:start
[Nemo] There is a way.

00:16:45.507 --> 00:16:48.175 position:10% line:83% align:start
They will most likely utilize
their large missile bay

00:16:48.208 --> 00:16:50.077 position:35% line:83% align:start
in order to
deliver their final blow.

00:16:50.110 --> 00:16:51.345 position:21% line:89% align:start
In order to do that,

00:16:51.378 --> 00:16:53.280 position:19% line:83% align:start
they will have to lower
the barrier, right?

00:16:53.313 --> 00:16:54.782 position:7% line:89% align:start
Right. Then we'll fire right up

00:16:54.816 --> 00:16:56.483 position:21% line:83% align:start
its launching tube at
that very moment.

00:16:56.518 --> 00:16:58.385 position:30% line:83% align:start
And after that,
it blows up, right?

00:16:58.418 --> 00:17:00.320 position:44% line:89% align:start
Yup.

00:17:00.354 --> 00:17:02.757 position:7% line:83% align:start
Thereby using Gargoyle's attack
to launch our counterattack.

00:17:02.790 --> 00:17:04.424 position:27% line:89% align:start
Don't be absurd.

00:17:04.458 --> 00:17:06.828 position:16% line:83% align:start
We don't even know where
that opening is going to be.

00:17:06.861 --> 00:17:10.330 position:16% line:83% align:start
-I'm sure we'll find it.
-So all we have to do is look.

00:17:10.364 --> 00:17:12.667 position:24% line:83% align:start
I say we must have
complete faith

00:17:12.700 --> 00:17:14.368 position:24% line:83% align:start
in the probability
of our success.

00:17:14.401 --> 00:17:17.104 position:10% line:89% align:start
Are you sure, sir, manually?

00:17:17.137 --> 00:17:18.773 position:35% line:89% align:start
Precisely.

00:17:18.806 --> 00:17:21.174 position:27% line:83% align:start
Our missile tube
must be opened by hand.

00:17:21.208 --> 00:17:22.476 position:21% line:89% align:start
See to it right away.

00:17:22.510 --> 00:17:24.478 position:38% line:89% align:start
Aye, aye.

00:17:24.512 --> 00:17:26.213 position:21% line:83% align:start
But who will be able
to aim it

00:17:26.246 --> 00:17:27.214 position:24% line:83% align:start
at the battleship's
missile tube?

00:17:27.247 --> 00:17:28.716 position:21% line:83% align:start
[Sanson] That you can
leave to us, Captain.

00:17:28.750 --> 00:17:30.117 position:47% line:89% align:start
Mm.

00:17:30.150 --> 00:17:32.654 position:13% line:89% align:start
[suspenseful music playing]

00:17:32.687 --> 00:17:34.522 position:27% line:83% align:start
We can get out of
here on the Gratan.

00:17:34.556 --> 00:17:36.824 position:10% line:83% align:start
Feel free to use this chance
to make a counterattack, sir.

00:17:39.794 --> 00:17:41.829 position:10% line:89% align:start
Arrivederci, my Captain Nemo.

00:17:43.363 --> 00:17:44.799 position:35% line:89% align:start
Bon voyage.

00:17:45.733 --> 00:17:47.835 position:10% line:89% align:start
Well, let's get out of here.

00:17:47.869 --> 00:17:49.369 position:24% line:83% align:start
-But before that...
-Huh?

00:17:49.403 --> 00:17:51.338 position:44% line:83% align:start
-Huh?
-[chuckles]

00:17:51.371 --> 00:17:52.640 position:41% line:89% align:start
[groan]

00:17:52.674 --> 00:17:54.141 position:41% line:89% align:start
[thuds]

00:17:54.174 --> 00:17:55.375 position:35% line:89% align:start
[clapping]

00:17:55.409 --> 00:17:56.844 position:13% line:89% align:start
But I want to go with you.

00:17:58.378 --> 00:18:00.414 position:35% line:83% align:start
-Forget it.
-Why not?

00:18:00.447 --> 00:18:03.618 position:24% line:83% align:start
Because I need you
to watch over the ladies.

00:18:03.651 --> 00:18:05.720 position:13% line:89% align:start
That's a man's duty, Jean.

00:18:05.753 --> 00:18:08.690 position:38% line:83% align:start
-But I--
-Listen, son.

00:18:08.723 --> 00:18:10.858 position:33% line:83% align:start
It's noble to
protect other people.

00:18:10.892 --> 00:18:13.260 position:30% line:83% align:start
But you have to
protect yourself, too.

00:18:14.596 --> 00:18:15.763 position:21% line:89% align:start
You have to survive.

00:18:15.797 --> 00:18:18.700 position:19% line:89% align:start
I see. You too, right?

00:18:18.733 --> 00:18:20.735 position:38% line:89% align:start
You bet.

00:18:20.768 --> 00:18:22.269 position:19% line:89% align:start
Good luck to you, Jean.

00:18:22.302 --> 00:18:24.137 position:21% line:89% align:start
[vehicle door whirs]

00:18:26.608 --> 00:18:29.276 position:10% line:83% align:start
[Sanson] We do live a rather
sordid life, do we not?

00:18:29.309 --> 00:18:31.579 position:33% line:83% align:start
[Hanson] Yup,
but we never get bored.

00:18:31.613 --> 00:18:33.848 position:13% line:89% align:start
Just as long as we survive.

00:18:33.881 --> 00:18:35.349 position:30% line:89% align:start
Well, let's go.

00:18:35.382 --> 00:18:36.517 position:33% line:83% align:start
-Yes, ma'am.
-Yes, ma'am.

00:18:36.551 --> 00:18:38.285 position:35% line:89% align:start
[screaming]

00:18:38.318 --> 00:18:39.286 position:10% line:83% align:start
-What's happening this time?
-What's happening this time?

00:18:39.319 --> 00:18:41.488 position:30% line:83% align:start
They're firing
Heavy Salvos at us, Captain.

00:18:43.558 --> 00:18:45.593 position:35% line:89% align:start
[explosion]

00:18:45.893 --> 00:18:47.260 position:38% line:89% align:start
Blast!

00:18:47.762 --> 00:18:49.564 position:10% line:83% align:start
The battleship won't need to
open its tube

00:18:49.597 --> 00:18:51.532 position:24% line:89% align:start
with this going on.

00:18:51.566 --> 00:18:54.769 position:13% line:83% align:start
Wait! Without electricity,
that hatch isn't going to open!

00:18:54.802 --> 00:18:56.638 position:27% line:83% align:start
Forget the hatch!
Blast right through!

00:18:56.671 --> 00:18:57.538 position:33% line:83% align:start
-You got it!
-You got it!

00:18:57.572 --> 00:18:59.306 position:35% line:89% align:start
[explosion]

00:18:59.339 --> 00:19:00.407 position:44% line:89% align:start
Whoo!

00:19:00.440 --> 00:19:02.610 position:35% line:89% align:start
[cheering]

00:19:02.644 --> 00:19:05.713 position:10% line:83% align:start
-Convert to flight mode two!
-[piano plays]

00:19:06.246 --> 00:19:07.447 position:38% line:89% align:start
[clicks]

00:19:07.481 --> 00:19:10.183 position:35% line:89% align:start
[whirring]

00:19:11.753 --> 00:19:13.821 position:16% line:89% align:start
[automatic weapons fire]

00:19:14.522 --> 00:19:15.590 position:38% line:89% align:start
[groans]

00:19:17.357 --> 00:19:19.292 position:30% line:83% align:start
The textite net
is already in place.

00:19:19.326 --> 00:19:22.329 position:10% line:83% align:start
-It should hold for a while.
-Then I guess I'll be going.

00:19:24.832 --> 00:19:27.502 position:10% line:83% align:start
Sorry, old chap, but we only
have one techno bomb left.

00:19:27.535 --> 00:19:30.571 position:24% line:83% align:start
-Good luck, Sanson!
-You can leave it to me.

00:19:30.605 --> 00:19:32.305 position:21% line:83% align:start
You see, I'm a bloody
genius with a gun!

00:19:32.339 --> 00:19:35.242 position:16% line:89% align:start
[automatic weapons fire]

00:19:35.275 --> 00:19:37.444 position:35% line:89% align:start
[explosion]

00:19:37.477 --> 00:19:39.781 position:5% line:83% align:start
[follower 1] She makes very good
shooting practice,

00:19:39.814 --> 00:19:41.281 position:10% line:89% align:start
does she not, Lord Gargoyle?

00:19:41.314 --> 00:19:42.650 position:44% line:89% align:start
Yes.

00:19:42.684 --> 00:19:44.952 position:27% line:83% align:start
I only wish you'd
quit missing the target.

00:19:44.986 --> 00:19:46.253 position:10% line:89% align:start
[follower 1] I'm sorry, sir.

00:19:46.286 --> 00:19:47.588 position:21% line:89% align:start
[Sanson] Wind speed?

00:19:47.622 --> 00:19:48.756 position:21% line:83% align:start
-[Hanson] Six meters.
-[Sanson] Temperature?

00:19:48.790 --> 00:19:50.323 position:7% line:89% align:start
[Hanson] 22 degrees centigrade!

00:19:50.357 --> 00:19:52.426 position:19% line:83% align:start
-[Sanson] Air pressure?
-[Hanson] 0.94.

00:19:52.459 --> 00:19:54.729 position:24% line:83% align:start
-[Sanson] Distance?
-[Hanson] 1.2 kilometers.

00:19:54.762 --> 00:19:57.665 position:7% line:83% align:start
Did it ever occur to you to put
protective armor on the cabin?

00:19:57.699 --> 00:19:59.834 position:30% line:83% align:start
When did I have
the time to do that?

00:20:00.568 --> 00:20:03.336 position:10% line:83% align:start
Open up and I'll blast it off
with a single shot.

00:20:05.807 --> 00:20:08.976 position:10% line:89% align:start
[all] One, two, three, four.

00:20:09.010 --> 00:20:12.580 position:16% line:83% align:start
We depend on this ship's
machinery entirely too much.

00:20:12.613 --> 00:20:15.583 position:16% line:83% align:start
Well, super-science isn't
much good when the power is cut.

00:20:15.616 --> 00:20:17.685 position:33% line:89% align:start
[explosions]

00:20:17.919 --> 00:20:19.954 position:38% line:89% align:start
[crying]

00:20:22.422 --> 00:20:24.625 position:10% line:83% align:start
[wireless 1] Second vertical
engine damaged!

00:20:24.659 --> 00:20:26.961 position:7% line:83% align:start
[wireless 2] There's no answer
from the starboard quarters!

00:20:26.994 --> 00:20:28.529 position:21% line:83% align:start
[helmsman] What about
the factory base?

00:20:28.563 --> 00:20:29.697 position:19% line:89% align:start
[wireless 3] No answer!

00:20:29.731 --> 00:20:30.898 position:16% line:89% align:start
It may have be destroyed.

00:20:30.932 --> 00:20:33.968 position:21% line:89% align:start
[explosions continue]

00:20:35.536 --> 00:20:36.704 position:41% line:89% align:start
Nadia!

00:20:39.439 --> 00:20:40.508 position:38% line:89% align:start
Stop it.

00:20:40.541 --> 00:20:41.709 position:30% line:89% align:start
Stop this now.

00:20:41.743 --> 00:20:42.977 position:10% line:89% align:start
I'll give you the Blue Water!

00:20:43.010 --> 00:20:44.846 position:10% line:89% align:start
Just stop killing each other.

00:20:45.947 --> 00:20:48.616 position:13% line:89% align:start
Lord Gargoyle, it's Nadia.

00:20:48.649 --> 00:20:49.984 position:44% line:89% align:start
Yes.

00:20:50.017 --> 00:20:51.786 position:5% line:89% align:start
I thought she might be on board.

00:20:51.819 --> 00:20:53.521 position:27% line:89% align:start
What shall we do?

00:20:55.556 --> 00:20:56.591 position:33% line:89% align:start
Fascinating.

00:20:56.624 --> 00:20:58.526 position:21% line:89% align:start
She is still useful.

00:20:58.559 --> 00:20:59.794 position:27% line:89% align:start
Bring her to me.

00:21:00.962 --> 00:21:02.997 position:30% line:89% align:start
[wave babbling]

00:21:03.531 --> 00:21:05.432 position:41% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

00:21:06.000 --> 00:21:07.334 position:41% line:89% align:start
Nadia!

00:21:07.367 --> 00:21:08.636 position:33% line:89% align:start
[Nadia] Jean!

00:21:10.037 --> 00:21:11.939 position:35% line:83% align:start
-[screams]
-Nadia!

00:21:12.707 --> 00:21:14.474 position:41% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

00:21:14.509 --> 00:21:16.010 position:27% line:83% align:start
[operator] Nadia
has been contained.

00:21:16.043 --> 00:21:18.613 position:10% line:89% align:start
I suppose this is checkmate.

00:21:19.080 --> 00:21:20.347 position:16% line:89% align:start
[follower 1] Understood.

00:21:20.380 --> 00:21:21.949 position:7% line:89% align:start
Prepare the annihilation bomb.

00:21:22.784 --> 00:21:26.554 position:16% line:83% align:start
The Emperor's Blue Water
will help us search for Nemo's,

00:21:26.587 --> 00:21:28.890 position:19% line:89% align:start
once they're destroyed.

00:21:29.590 --> 00:21:32.425 position:13% line:89% align:start
[suspenseful music playing]

00:21:34.729 --> 00:21:35.563 position:35% line:89% align:start
That's it.

00:21:41.468 --> 00:21:43.571 position:35% line:89% align:start
[explosion]

00:21:43.604 --> 00:21:45.472 position:35% line:89% align:start
[screaming]

00:21:49.409 --> 00:21:50.645 position:16% line:89% align:start
[helmsman] Bow destroyed.

00:21:50.678 --> 00:21:52.113 position:35% line:83% align:start
If we take
another one like that,

00:21:52.146 --> 00:21:54.015 position:16% line:83% align:start
it will be the last sound
any of us will hear, sir.

00:21:56.449 --> 00:21:57.718 position:30% line:89% align:start
[Sanson] Blast!

00:21:57.752 --> 00:21:59.821 position:19% line:83% align:start
They've already loaded
the next launch tube.

00:21:59.854 --> 00:22:01.923 position:24% line:83% align:start
Hey, can't you hold
this thing steady?

00:22:01.956 --> 00:22:03.958 position:30% line:89% align:start
[all] Heave-ho!

00:22:05.760 --> 00:22:07.394 position:38% line:83% align:start
-Take it.
-Right!

00:22:08.029 --> 00:22:10.097 position:30% line:83% align:start
I know I'll get
it on the next round.

00:22:11.464 --> 00:22:13.634 position:16% line:83% align:start
-[indistinct] Oh, my God.
-[gun clicks]

00:22:13.668 --> 00:22:16.938 position:10% line:83% align:start
[Sanson] This is one miracle
I can perform myself.

00:22:18.471 --> 00:22:20.407 position:33% line:89% align:start
[explosions]

00:22:20.440 --> 00:22:21.742 position:35% line:89% align:start
[laughter]

00:22:21.776 --> 00:22:23.410 position:33% line:89% align:start
[air hissing]

00:22:23.443 --> 00:22:25.112 position:33% line:83% align:start
-[all] Whoa.
-[Sanson] What?

00:22:25.146 --> 00:22:26.981 position:35% line:89% align:start
[screaming]

00:22:29.951 --> 00:22:33.087 position:19% line:89% align:start
[all] Somebody help us.

00:22:33.120 --> 00:22:34.856 position:33% line:89% align:start
[grunts] Go!

00:22:34.889 --> 00:22:37.091 position:33% line:89% align:start
[engine revs]

00:22:37.592 --> 00:22:39.126 position:47% line:89% align:start
Go!

00:22:40.661 --> 00:22:42.495 position:33% line:89% align:start
[explosions]

00:22:43.965 --> 00:22:45.498 position:30% line:89% align:start
[Nadia screams]

00:22:46.734 --> 00:22:48.636 position:27% line:89% align:start
Well done. Bravo.

00:22:50.671 --> 00:22:51.839 position:16% line:89% align:start
Fire the blaster missile.

00:22:51.873 --> 00:22:53.541 position:30% line:89% align:start
[electric zaps]

00:22:55.509 --> 00:22:57.144 position:35% line:89% align:start
[explosion]

00:23:00.848 --> 00:23:03.684 position:13% line:83% align:start
The battle ship's magnetic
force is weakening, sir.

00:23:06.721 --> 00:23:07.788 position:19% line:89% align:start
We're falling seaward.

00:23:07.822 --> 00:23:08.990 position:5% line:89% align:start
All hands, take crash positions.

00:23:10.892 --> 00:23:12.727 position:27% line:89% align:start
[water splashes]

00:23:16.764 --> 00:23:20.801 position:21% line:83% align:start
-How did this happen?
-I am most sorry, sir.

00:23:20.835 --> 00:23:22.469 position:38% line:89% align:start
Spare me.

00:23:22.503 --> 00:23:24.939 position:5% line:89% align:start
I'll discuss your penalty later.

00:23:24.972 --> 00:23:26.140 position:35% line:89% align:start
Understood.

00:23:27.108 --> 00:23:29.043 position:35% line:83% align:start
[Gargoyle]
She won't last long now.

00:23:29.911 --> 00:23:31.979 position:13% line:83% align:start
Order a Garfish to deliver
the coup de grace.

00:23:32.013 --> 00:23:33.581 position:35% line:89% align:start
Understood.

00:23:33.614 --> 00:23:35.883 position:16% line:83% align:start
[operator 1] The Nautilus
is sinking fast.

00:23:36.918 --> 00:23:39.754 position:27% line:89% align:start
[water babbling]

00:23:42.890 --> 00:23:46.594 position:13% line:89% align:start
Thus is the fate of fools.

00:23:55.670 --> 00:23:56.504 position:21% line:89% align:start
[singing in Japanese]

